'''''Akbuzat''''' ({{lang-ba|Аҡбуҙат}}, from Ak is "white" + Turkic буҙат "Curly Horse") is the most famous ''kubair'' ([[epic poetry|epic poem]]) of the [[Bashkirs]]. It is analog many similar epics (the [[Pegasus]]).
[[File: Flag of Kigi rayon (Bashkortostan).png|thumb|300px|The Curly Horse of Akbuzat on the Flag of Kigi rayon|right]]
== Plot == The main hero of Akbuzat epic poem is Hauban. He went to the Underwater kingdom for search the сurly horse Akbuzat and diamond sword.
