'''Dargin writing''' is a written form of communication representing the North East Caucasian [[Dargin language]]. This language has approximately 439,000 speakers, most of whom live in the Russian republic of [[Dagestan]]. Additionally, Darlin writing is used in the Russian Republics of [[Kalmykia]], [[Khanty-Mansi Autonomous Okrug|Khantia-Mansia]], and [[Chechnya]], as well as nearby countries of [[Azerbaijan]], [[Kazakhstan]], [[Kyrgyzstan]], [[Turkey]], [[Turkmenistan]], [[Ukraine]], and [[Uzbekistan]]. <ref>{{Cite web|title =Dargwa.|url =https://www.omniglot.com/writing/dargwa.htm|accessdate = March 10, 2018|publisher = Omniglot.|date =1998}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last= Minahan|first= James|date= 2000|title= One Europe, Many Nations: A Historical Dictionary of European National Groups |publisher= Greenwood Publishing Group |access-date= March 10, 2018}}</ref>
== History == The Arabic alphabet was adapted as the Dargin phonetics alphabet in 1920, but it was poorly adapted to the sounds of the [[Ukrainian language]]. So in 1928, as part of the All-Union project on [[Romanization]], the [[Latin-based alphabet]] was adopted for Dargin. In the same year, the first primer in this alphabet was published (cupanov r. Nuşala ʐaꝗ-sawet. Mәħәc-qala, 1928). Initially the Dargin Romanized alphabet had no capital letters. After the reform of 1932 capital letters were introduced, some Latin letters were excluded and the alphabet took the form shown in the table: {| style="font-family:Arial Unicode MS; font-size:1.4em; border-color:#000000; border-width:1px; border-style:solid; border-collapse:collapse; background-color:#F8F8EF" | style="width:3em;" | A a | style="width:3em;" | B b | style="width:3em;" | C c | style="width:3em;" | Ç ç | style="width:3em;" | D d | style="width:3em;" | E e | style="width:3em;" | Ә ә | style="width:3em;" | F f |- | style="width:3em;" | G g | style="width:3em;" | Ƣ ƣ | style="width:3em;" | H h | style="width:3em;" | Ⱨ ⱨ | style="width:3em;" | Ħ ħ | style="width:3em;" | I i | style="width:3em;" | J j | style="width:3em;" | K k |- | style="width:3em;" | Ⱪ ⱪ | style="width:3em;" | L l | style="width:3em;" | M m | style="width:3em;" | N n | style="width:3em;" | O o | style="width:3em;" | P p | style="width:3em;" | Q q | style="width:3em;" | Ꝗ ꝗ |- | style="width:3em;" | R r | style="width:3em;" | S s | style="width:3em;" | Ş ş | style="width:3em;" | S̷ s̷ | style="width:3em;" | T t | style="width:3em;" | T̨ t̨ | style="width:3em;" | U u | style="width:3em;" | V v |- | style="width:3em;" | X x | style="width:3em;" | Ҳ ҳ | style="width:3em;" | Ӿ ӿ | style="width:3em;" | Z z | style="width:3em;" | Ⱬ ⱬ | style="width:3em;" | Ƶ ƶ | style="width:3em;" | Ⱬ̵ ⱬ̵ | style="width:3em;" | Ӡ ӡ |}
