'''Lamont Stephenson''' (born April 2, 1975) is an American criminal who was added to the [[FBI Ten Most Wanted Fugitives]] list on October 11, 2018. He is wanted for the murder of his fiancee, Olga Dejesus, in [[Newark, New Jersey]] in October of 2014. The FBI is offering a reward of $100,000 for his capture.<ref>https://www.fbi.gov/wanted/topten/lamont-stephenson</ref>

